  <brief_title>Multi-frequency Bioelectrical Impedance for Estimating Total Body Water by Deuterium Dilution</brief_title>
  <official_title>Utility of Multi-frequency Bioelectrical Impedance Compared to Deuterium Dilution for Assessment of Total Body Water</official_title>
