  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      SPECIFIC AIM:

      Determine the validity of the Biospace bioelectrical impedance devices compared to deuterium
      water (D2O) measurements.

      HYPOTHESIS:

      The Biospace Body Composition Analyzers are valid tools for measuring total body water and
      body composition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
